ts/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有線新聞暫時唔會變下個CCTVB</blockquote><br />\n都執啦，變唔變又有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87649e839027bb1e03ec5fa50c6f3c51bc2be2ec","tid":149371,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:51:42.000Z","msg":"最尾個句，意思即係等收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4791e08ecf06324cb93dca2c17143e8ff37c5ff7","tid":149371,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗倉講明唔包底<br />\n<br />\n遲早變亞視又要撲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直接執柒左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ed80c48340fcf1cf39bfff1d736dc9864e6aa1","tid":149371,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有線新聞暫時唔會變下個CCTVB</blockquote><br />\n只係報道形式、畫面規格貼近大台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b724916d00c1640a9c074ae822b9e146dd2888","tid":149371,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:52:59.000Z","msg":"有線新聞好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e0d7d8651e9cb8d8d76f4744763d830cfcd4c4","tid":149371,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:53:52.000Z","msg":"九龍倉都cut唔到有線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa279fb69f5b347b993d32c574a16cad2a973f5","tid":149371,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最尾個句，意思即係等收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"ccfc4b1d847c050ef3674cb05fb675b9b14320a9","tid":149371,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有線新聞暫時唔會變下個CCTVB</blockquote><br />\n只係報道形式、畫面規格貼近大台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼到時奇妙開台 有得睇下有線新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be34cf9ddf93c64e82d2682e771b3f926839bb7e","tid":149371,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:03:06.000Z","msg":"姐係做執笠？"},{"pid":"d3c1ab675b9f267091be350feda617ab1074876c","tid":149371,"uid":26224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最尾個句，意思即係等收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家返屋企開電視都係睇有線新聞..<br />\n連有線新聞都無埋... <br />\n返到屋企重有乜野娛樂...<br />\n<br />\n留係香港重有乜意思."},{"pid":"7b1d71e93ca3d3a562f4351c54a871133061c3e0","tid":149371,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:03:44.000Z","msg":"wiki買？"},{"pid":"e1227a66f49ac8f5c0032b89a93be908c8e03690","tid":149371,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"HKTV出手？"},{"pid":"08741ecf9b97aa79431f9d30e5e8adcdc961d96d","tid":149371,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:06:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>九龍倉都cut唔到有線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db9cc8321a4e87f754bcd13b8b60bebe71c2ccc","tid":149371,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:06:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HKTV出手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有得考慮咼"},{"pid":"d819cc6275a18bdac7b655722dbe5621e2f22e7d","tid":149371,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:07:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姐係做執笠？</blockquote><br />\n唔係即時執<br />\n<br />\n要睇九倉個承諾期到幾時"},{"pid":"8cf78a39512fcfe44d4af0388d8433a2cd650d28","tid":149371,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:08:05.000Z","msg":"即係執笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1954cca83d6d57d3fb1b120d490116384b44be7","tid":149371,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>HKTV出手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有得考慮咼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n奇妙電視係獨立公司申請喎，資金都唔同。<br />\n<br />\n要賣一早可以賣啦，我覺得九倉佢地獨立投資者未必諗著賣。"},{"pid":"b5561d270ac41d071fb745cabf3ebd9b2f1f7358","tid":149371,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>姐係做執笠？</blockquote><br />\n唔係即時執<br />\n<br />\n要睇九倉個承諾期到幾時</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個個月蝕1-2千個<br />\n<br />\n唔頂得好耐，嚟梗應該會有栽員潮，節流先。"},{"pid":"8aaf7b2950f649b4f3d81ffd2f243748d08204fd","tid":149371,"uid":11805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:09:18.000Z","msg":"即係燒哂餘下資金就game over<br />\n除非有新投資者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc665ae5924a6bc7d637a3489eb1238e51230af","tid":149371,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗倉講明唔包底<br />\n<br />\n遲早變亞視又要撲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n狗倉之前先賣左電訊，而家連I cable 都唔要，電訊業正式玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037775b84082a3c87281ea7159895fff361f363a","tid":149371,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係燒哂餘下資金就game over<br />\n除非有新投資者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年都話負債6-7億..<br />\n<br />\n年年蝕兩億"},{"pid":"e07da0c392048d93a40931c8bd7df1abdeb0ac5d","tid":149371,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即係燒哂餘下資金就game over<br />\n除非有新投資者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年都話負債6-7億..<br />\n<br />\n年年蝕兩億</blockquote><br />\n1097供股咪得囉"},{"pid":"3d4f9cbec2d5b9e06905123da2c04666d6559115","tid":149371,"uid":11805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即係燒哂餘下資金就game over<br />\n除非有新投資者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年都話負債6-7億..<br />\n<br />\n年年蝕兩億</blockquote><br />\n2億對九倉黎講係碎銀<br />\n我諗真係唔想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74835fdfe957680fbb434da672336a8f21d7726","tid":149371,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>HKTV出手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有得考慮咼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n奇妙電視係獨立公司申請喎，資金都唔同。<br />\n<br />\n要賣一早可以賣啦，我覺得九倉佢地獨立投資者未必諗著賣。</blockquote><br />\n奇妙係有記子公司，唔係獨立嫁。<br />\n當初入紙支請都係有記代表佢同政府入紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c316a8dbb93e561a95c08b93f8f8fa190d58ef0","tid":149371,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"Hktv做咩唔出手"},{"pid":"15e6876ba6e1660a9169a97334dc7ac286de2600","tid":149371,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hktv做咩唔出手</blockquote><br />\n等下屆特首上台掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw hktv4月搬廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949f90efd5bdd7a09394a0e6cc5b657ac4739529","tid":149371,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>狗倉講明唔包底<br />\n<br />\n遲早變亞視又要撲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n狗倉之前先賣左電訊，而家連I cable 都唔要，電訊業正式玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今次直情講明全線走鬼<br />\n<br />\n都好正常，全部業務賺又無咩理由留蝕本生意"},{"pid":"50ea6706f2b99b9709d1d61a05e36c6a6e9fc7d7","tid":149371,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>HKTV出手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有得考慮咼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n奇妙電視係獨立公司申請喎，資金都唔同。<br />\n<br />\n要賣一早可以賣啦，我覺得九倉佢地獨立投資者未必諗著賣。</blockquote><br />\n奇妙係有記子公司，唔係獨立嫁。<br />\n當初入紙支請都係有記代表佢同政府入紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n後尾唔係了，所以先出到牌。<br />\n<br />\n2016年3月9日，九龍倉集團主席兼常務董事吳天海表示，奇妙電視已進行股權重組以符合《廣播條例》規定，將會提交相關證明予通訊局，再由行政會議作出發牌決定。重組後，有線寬頻於奇妙電視的表決權不多於15%。"},{"pid":"87ffea783df2de8599e1f00dd4a8490d427cc2c8","tid":149371,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:19:39.000Z","msg":"賣唔去，又唔投資，想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19934314a0d995687f7997e894a9dce417639b1c","tid":149371,"uid":24697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:21:41.000Z","msg":"賣多幾間樓錢響到"},{"pid":"4332f4578f24eec4f24c4e6245de77a704b00e25","tid":149371,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賣唔去，又唔投資，想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法律上兩間上市公司，唔投資又吹佢唔漲<br />\n<br />\n我睇隨時慘過亞視，連有版權賣比人嘅節目都好少"},{"pid":"1228439a2eaa27841b637c1dcf411d82b3897011","tid":149371,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:28:36.000Z","msg":"有線寬頻:已收到九倉不再提供資金承擔通知<br />\n<br />\n港交所原文:<a href=\"http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/SEHK/2017/0309/LTN20170309276_C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkexnews.hk%2Flistedco%2Flistconews%2FSEHK%2F2017%2F0309%2FLTN20170309276_C.pdf&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9onIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=fed6c5d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/SEHK/2017/0309/LTN20170309276_C.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"a74a9d33e5a1e2bf5a88adfdd503d1f182f25359","tid":149371,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>賣唔去，又唔投資，想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法律上兩間上市公司，唔投資又吹佢唔漲<br />\n<br />\n我睇隨時慘過亞視，連有版權賣比人嘅節目都好少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢兩年仲洗多過億玩高清新聞台，真係揼錢落海。"},{"pid":"4d299c8e1d102a6641f98cd9228b0067292a4322","tid":149371,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:32:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾到連中資都唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3aa7ebf4fb12c69336b6acd130837d474f438ca","tid":149371,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:36:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有線寬頻:已收到九倉不再提供資金承擔通知<br />\n<br />\n港交所原文:<a href=\"http://www